OL,6,FA 17th century estate in Shropshire,
OL,7,Fwhich is owned by the founder of the
OL,8,Fdiscount store Poundland, has gone up
OL,9,Ffor sale.
OL,11,FKeith Smith bought Ludstone Hall In
OL,12,Fthe late 1990s but now after many
OL,13,Fyears the family has decided to cash
OL,14,Fin and move on.
OL,16,FBuilt in 1607, the Jacobean mansion is
OL,17,Fa mix of old & new, with the odd quirk
OL,18,Ftoo.
