OL,6,FIt has 9 bedrooms, 4 reception rooms,
OL,7,F7 bathrooms, a cellar, dining room, &
OL,8,Fbar and within its walls there's a
OL,9,Fmuseum dedicated to Poundland.
OL,11,FThe building also has an indoor
OL,12,Fswimming pool with a retractable floor.
OL,14,FOver the years the family - and owners
OL,15,Fof the business born from selling
OL,16,Feverything for #1 - spent more than
OL,17,Ftwo and a half million pounds
OL,18,Frenovating the property.
